# Virtual Assistant (HTML / CSS / JavaScript)

This is a simple virtual assistant built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
The assistant can take input from the user and reply with basic responses.  
It works inside the browser without any backend or database.

## ✨ Features
- Simple and clean UI
- User can type queries
- Predefined responses using JavaScript
- Instant reply in chat format
- Lightweight and easy to customize

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **HTML** – Structure of the webpage  
- **CSS** – Styling and layout  
- **JavaScript** – Logic and response handling  

## 🚀 How to Run
1. Download or clone the project.
2. Open `index.html` in any browser.
3. Start typing your queries in the chat box.

## ✅ Example Questions
- "Hello"
- "What is your name?"
- "Who created you?"
- "How are you?"

